## T_8: Update Main to include Caregiver module

````java path=src/main/java/de/hitec/nhplus/Main.java mode=EDIT
// Add this method to the Main class to create the caregiver view
private void showAllCaregiverView() {
 try {
 FXMLLoader loader = new FXMLLoader(Main.class.getResource("/de/hitec/nhplus/AllCaregiverView.fxml"));
 AnchorPane pane = loader.load();
 mainLayout.setCenter(pane);
 } catch (IOException e) {
 e.printStackTrace();
 }
}

// Update the initialize method to add the caregiver menu item
private void initialize() {
 // Existing code...

 // Add caregiver menu item
 MenuItem caregiverMenuItem = new MenuItem("Pflegekräfte");
 caregiverMenuItem.setOnAction(event -> showAllCaregiverView());

 // Add to the menu
 fileMenu.getItems().add(caregiverMenuItem);
 // Or if you have a separate menu for data:
 // dataMenu.getItems().add(caregiverMenuItem);
}
