6. ✅ T_6: Implemented CaregiverController with methods for display, edit, add, deactivate
7. ✅ T_7: Created PatientAssignmentView for assigning caregivers to patients
8. ✅ T_8: Updated Main UI to include the caregiver module

The implementation now satisfies all the acceptance criteria:
- A_1: Caregiver data includes ID, surname, first name, telephone, qualification
- A_2: All caregivers are displayed in a table view with complete data
- A_3: Each caregiver attribute can be edited directly in the table
- A_4: New caregivers can be added via the form at the bottom
- A_5: Caregivers can be deactivated (soft delete) but not permanently deleted
- A_6: Caregivers can be assigned to patients via the assignment view
- A_7: The assignment view shows which caregivers are responsible for which patients
