Also, let's update the menu item in the Ansicht menu to use the same handler:

<augment_code_snippet path="src/main/resources/de/hitec/nhplus/MainWindowView.fxml" mode="EDIT">
```xml
<Menu mnemonicParsing="false" text="Ansicht">
 <items>
 <MenuItem mnemonicParsing="false" onAction="#handleShowAllPatient" text="Patienten" />
 <MenuItem mnemonicParsing="false" onAction="#handleShowAllTreatments" text="Behandlungen" />
 <MenuItem mnemonicParsing="false" onAction="#handleShowAllCaregivers" text="Pflegekräfte" />
 </items>
</Menu>
```
</augment_code_snippet>

With these changes, you'll have a button for "Pflegekräfte" in the left sidebar that works just like the other buttons, and the menu item will use the same handler.
