To run your application, you should use one of these methods:

1. Use Maven to run the application:
 ```
 mvn clean javafx:run
 ```

2. If you're running from IntelliJ IDEA, make sure to add VM options to your run configuration:
 ```
 --module-path "path\to\javafx-sdk\lib" --add-modules javafx.controls,javafx.fxml
 ```

3. You can also add a simple shell script to run the application:

<augment_code_snippet path="run.bat" mode="EDIT">
```batch
@echo off
