```
</augment_code_snippet>

Replace `C:\path\to\javafx-sdk\lib` with the actual path to your JavaFX SDK lib directory. You can download the JavaFX SDK from https://gluonhq.com/products/javafx/ if you don't have it already.

This error occurs because JavaFX is no longer bundled with the JDK since Java 11, so you need to explicitly include the JavaFX modules when running the application.
