<augment_code_snippet path="src/main/java/de/hitec/nhplus/controller/PatientAssignmentController.java" mode="EDIT">
```java
@FXML
public void handleClose() {
 // Get the stage from the button
 Stage stage = (Stage) btnClose.getScene().getWindow();
 // Close the window
 stage.close();
}
```
</augment_code_snippet>

This pattern is consistent with how other close/cancel buttons work in your application, like in the `TreatmentController` where the `handleCancel()` method closes the stage.
